      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2004 BMW M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s machine featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings across the multi-link rear suspension. Mechanically, the car is dialed in; the S54 pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with no hesitation, and the cooling system has been overhauled to prevent typical heat-cycle fatigue. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance are top-tier. Recent compression tests show strong, even numbers across all six cylinders, ensuring this M3 is ready for technical canyon runs or daily spirited commutes.",
